{"id":"lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MjA0Mw_0003","text":"仍然是心中有鬼 即使吻她會折壽仍未貴","structure":{"line_index":3,"char_count":17},"semantics":{"themes":["愛情","罪惡感","犧牲"],"sentiment":"VERY_NEGATIVE","keywords":["心中有鬼","折壽","未貴"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,0,2,3,3,5,9,3,9,5,3,4,2,0,2,4],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["jing4","jin4","si6","sam1","zung1","jau5","gwai2","zik1","si2","man5","taa1","zit3","sau6","jing4","mei6","gwai3"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"仍然","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"是","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"心中有鬼","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"即使","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"吻","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"她","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"會","pos":"AUX"},{"text":"折壽","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"仍未貴","pos":"ADJ"}],"syntax_notes":"『心中有鬼』為慣用語，表達內疚感。『即使...仍未貴』為讓步複句，強調即使付出生命代價也覺得值得。"},"source":{"title":"先走爲敬","artists":["陳小春"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Mandopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2043","prev_line_id":"lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MjA0Mw_0002","next_line_id":"lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MjA0Mw_0004","paragraph_id":"para_01"}}
{"id":"lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MjA0Mw_0004","text":"若是愛換不到歡笑一世","structure":{"line_index":4,"char_count":10},"semantics":{"themes":["愛情","痛苦","無奈"],"sentiment":"VERY_NEGATIVE","keywords":["愛換","歡笑","一世"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[2,2,4,2,3,4,3,4,3,4],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["joek6","si6","oi3","wun6","bat1","dou3","fun1","siu3","jat1","sai3"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"若","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"是","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"愛換","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"不到","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"歡笑","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"一世","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"『若是』引導假設語氣，『一世』強調時間的長度。"},"source":{"title":"先走爲敬","artists":["陳小春"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Mandopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2043","prev_line_id":"lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MjA0Mw_0003","next_line_id":"lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MjA0Mw_0005","paragraph_id":"para_01"}}
{"id":"lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MjA0Mw_0005","text":"愛到痛苦仍能成爲安慰","structure":{"line_index":5,"char_count":10},"semantics":{"themes":["愛情","痛苦","安慰"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["痛苦","安慰"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[4,4,4,9,0,0,0,3,4],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["oi3","dou3","tung3","fu2","jing4","nang4","sing4","on1","wai3"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"愛到","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"痛苦","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"仍能","pos":"AUX"},{"text":"成爲","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"安慰","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"『仍能』表示即使在痛苦中也能找到慰藉，語氣帶有自我麻痺的意味。"},"source":{"title":"先走爲敬","artists":["陳小春"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Mandopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2043","prev_line_id":"lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MjA0Mw_0004","next_line_id":"lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MjA0Mw_0006","paragraph_id":"para_01"}}
{"id":"lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MjA0Mw_0006","text":"不要任性 自虐是我的個性","structure":{"line_index":6,"char_count":11},"semantics":{"themes":["自我認知","個性","自虐"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["任性","自虐","個性"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[3,4,2,4,2,2,2,5,3,4,4],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["bat1","jiu3","jam6","sing3","zi6","joek6","si6","ngo5","dik1","go3","sing3"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"不要","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"任性","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"自虐","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"是","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"的","pos":"PART"},{"text":"個性","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"『不要』為否定祈使句，強調對自身行為的否定。『自虐是我的個性』直接點明主題。"},"source":{"title":"先走爲敬","artists":["陳小春"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Mandopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2043","prev_line_id":"lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MjA0Mw_0005","next_line_id":"lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MjA0Mw_0007","paragraph_id":"para_01"}}
