{"id":"lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MjA0Mw_0011","text":"一擠身於這種三角便到盡頭","structure":{"line_index":11,"char_count":12},"semantics":{"themes":["愛情","困境","結局"],"sentiment":"VERY_NEGATIVE","keywords":["三角","盡頭"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[3,3,3,3,5,9,3,4,2,4,2,0],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["jat1","zai1","san1","jyu1","ze5","zung2","saam1","gok3","bin6","dou3","zeon6","tau4"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"一","pos":"NUM"},{"text":"擠身於","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"這種","pos":"DET"},{"text":"三角","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"便","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"到","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"盡頭","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"『一擠身於這種三角』描述陷入三角關係的處境。『便到盡頭』預示悲劇性的結局。"},"source":{"title":"先走爲敬","artists":["陳小春"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Mandopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2043","prev_line_id":"lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MjA0Mw_0010","next_line_id":"lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MjA0Mw_0012","paragraph_id":"para_02"}}
{"id":"lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MjA0Mw_0012","text":"好歹都想花都拖過那一雙手","structure":{"line_index":12,"char_count":12},"semantics":{"themes":["愛情","渴望","遺憾"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["花都","拖手"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[9,9,3,9,3,3,3,4,5,3,3,9],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["hou2","daai2","dou1","soeng2","faa1","dou1","to1","gwo3","naa5","jat1","soeng1","sau2"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"好歹","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"都","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"想","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"花都","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"拖過","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"那","pos":"DET"},{"text":"一","pos":"NUM"},{"text":"雙手","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"『好歹』表示無論如何。『花都拖過那一雙手』是具體描寫，表達對親密接觸的渴望。"},"source":{"title":"先走爲敬","artists":["陳小春"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Mandopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2043","prev_line_id":"lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MjA0Mw_0011","next_line_id":"lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MjA0Mw_0013","paragraph_id":"para_02"}}
{"id":"lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MjA0Mw_0013","text":"逼得她跟他分手我便如同妖獸","structure":{"line_index":13,"char_count":13},"semantics":{"themes":["愛情","破壞","痛苦"],"sentiment":"VERY_NEGATIVE","keywords":["分手","妖獸"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[3,3,3,3,3,3,9,5,2,0,0,3,4],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["bik1","dak1","taa1","gan1","taa1","fan1","sau2","ngo5","bin6","jyu4","tung4","jiu1","sau3"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"逼得","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"她","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"跟","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"他","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"分手","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"便","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"如同","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"妖獸","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"『逼得...分手』描述自己造成的後果。『我便如同妖獸』將自己比喻為破壞者，情感強烈。"},"source":{"title":"先走爲敬","artists":["陳小春"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Mandopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2043","prev_line_id":"lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MjA0Mw_0012","next_line_id":"lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MjA0Mw_0014","paragraph_id":"para_02"}}
{"id":"lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MjA0Mw_0014","text":"人苦戀當然不講理由","structure":{"line_index":14,"char_count":9},"semantics":{"themes":["愛情","苦戀","執著"],"sentiment":"VERY_NEGATIVE","keywords":["苦戀","理由"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,9,9,0,3,9,5,0],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["jan4","fu2","lyun2","jin4","bat1","gong2","lei5","jau4"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"人","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"苦戀","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"當然","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"不","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"講","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"理由","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"『人苦戀當然不講理由』是對苦戀行為的解釋，帶有宿命感。"},"source":{"title":"先走爲敬","artists":["陳小春"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Mandopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2043","prev_line_id":"lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MjA0Mw_0013","next_line_id":"lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MjA0Mw_0015","paragraph_id":"para_02"}}
